        {
            "title": "川普警告伊朗戰爭升級,亞洲股市下跌;南韓領跌",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Nvib4xSMzsyQIvZwgu7Dkw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXNPEAAG092_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com- 週四亞洲股市下跌,扭轉了4月強勁開局的走勢,因美國總統唐納德·川普警告未來兩到三週伊朗戰爭將升級。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">南韓KOSPI指數表現最差,儘管前一交易日錄得強勁漲幅,而日本股市也出現大幅下跌。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">亞洲市場最初從華爾街隔夜的積極表現中獲得了一些正面信號。但在川普發表評論後,標普500指數期貨下跌超過1%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>川普警告伊朗戰爭升級後,KOSPI和日經指數領跌</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">南韓KOSPI指數是亞洲表現最差的股市,下跌3.7%,而日本日經225指數和東證指數分別下跌2%和1.2%。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-f0e7e2b8-1d56-3266-a541-8692c244f192-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">日本和南韓股市基本上扭轉了前一交易日的強勁反彈,並回落至3月份的低點附近。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這兩個市場在週三領漲亞洲市場,此前3月份遭受重創。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在川普表示美國將在未來兩到三週內加大對伊朗的軍事行動後,市場風險偏好迅速惡化,粉碎了先前對戰爭降級的希望。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普表示,美國將在未來幾週內「極其猛烈地」打擊伊朗,並呼籲德黑蘭要麼接受停火,要麼面臨美國對其電力基礎設施的打擊。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在談到荷莫茲海峽時,川普表示美國不會推動重新開放該通道,並呼籲依賴荷莫茲海峽的國家要麼從美國購買石油,要麼自行重新開放該通道。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>亞洲股市因伊朗相關干擾持續而下滑</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">週四亞洲市場普遍下跌,扭轉了前一交易日的強勁反彈。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">中國滬深300指數和上證綜合指數分別下跌0.7%和0.5%,而科技股的再度下跌拖累恆生指數下跌1%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">澳洲ASX 200指數下跌1.1%,對2月份好於預期的貿易收支數據反應平淡,該數據顯示出口大幅增長。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">新加坡海峽時報指數下跌0.7%,而印度Nifty 50指數期貨下跌1.6%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在川普發表評論後,油價上漲高達5%,因市場認為能源市場持續受到干擾的情況幾乎沒有緩解。荷莫茲海峽是多個亞洲主要經濟體的石油和天然氣運輸關鍵來源。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">油價上漲預計也將導致未來幾個月通膨走高——這一趨勢可能促使全球主要央行採取更加鷹派的立場。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E6%88%B0%E7%88%AD%E5%8D%87%E7%B4%9A-%E4%BA%9E%E6%B4%B2%E8%82%A1%E5%B8%82%E4%B8%8B%E8%B7%8C-%E5%8D%97%E9%9F%93%E9%A0%98%E8%B7%8C-045222196.html",
